QuestData.Title: Skymistress Gloaming
QuestData.Description: It doesn't look as if you have a cart or a beast of burden with you, so I'd better send you back only with what you can carry. If you've spoken with Skymaster Brightdawn at Fairbreeze Village, then you should get this to Sathiel as soon as possible by flying back.$B$BTake these goods for final inspection to Skymistress Gloaming just outside Silvermoon City's Shepherd's Gate.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Sathiel's Goods to Skymistress Gloaming just outside Silvermoon City's Shepherd's Gate.
QuestData.CompletionText: Wow, that box of goods you have there looks heavy! You want to load that up on one of my flying beauties?
QuestData.RewardText: Back down to Fairbreeze Village in Eversong Woods, then? Sure, I can get you there fast!
